Megatron Revived:

The clone looked down on Perceptor with a sneer.  He then laughed out loud at the treacherous robot.
&quot;You are no Decepticon.  My Matrix tells me differant.  You are a treacherous Autobot, just like that sniveling Starscream, full of treason and schemes.  Go back to your hole in the wall, I have no need to hear you rant on the identity of Hydras.&quot;
Megatron Revived then turned and looked at Maxima.  A curiosity, she could be a great leader.  He could use someone like her back in the Fleet.
&quot;Hydras is a throwback.  A mistake.  He is a combination of Quintesson programming and Unicron&#39;s lunacy.  He is no leader.  I&#39;ll even go as far as to say he doesn&#39;t even have a Matrix Chamber.&quot;
He smirked and brought a hand to the center of his chest, where a highly stylized purple insignia resided.
&quot;True Cybertronian Leaders are more capable than he.  Why do you stay with him?  Do you like living in fear, fear he will one day destroy you with out a single thought?  He can do that, he is more than capable to do so.&quot; 

MaximaSR74@... wrote:
Watching the Megatron clone with her crimson gaze, cool & calculated... 

Then shot a glare at Perceptor. He didn&#39;t seem to assist the situation any. An animal growl towards him, &quot;Watch your metallic tongue, Perceptor. Or you will soon enough find it missing!&quot; 

Then returning her fiery crimson optics back upon the Clone. &quot;Forgive him. He is alike the others. Predacons know little of old Decepticon discipline.&quot; 

Looking him over as she walked towards him... &quot;You claim to be Megatron.. yet,&quot; then started to circle around him in a feline manner, &quot;you claim you are not.&quot;

Come back around to the front to face him. &quot;Confusion will not work,&quot; smirking with a purr, placing her long claw hand units upon her hips as the wings flexed a moment. 


